<A>__{gun at the ready, atwood edges her way downward. at about the tenth step she is able to lean over and look through the banisters. meeks and the woman are propping themselves up against the wall on the landing below. both of them still have their guns. the moment meeks' eyes meet atwood's, he puts his gun to the woman heads. bang! atwood sucks in her breath. meeks puts the gun to his temple. bang! atwood clasps a hand to her mouth and exhales in ragged gulps.}
